{"tid":772210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸仔驚覺家中漏煤氣　抽煙定驚引發爆炸","createTime":"2018-08-08T14:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T12:24:37.000Z","uid":122,"like":1431,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5340a6086978bd66c4f21dcaf5e81baac46708","tid":772210,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"山西男驚覺家中漏煤氣　抽煙定驚引發爆炸<br />\n<br />\n山西陽泉市平定縣一名男子回家時，聽到煤氣警報器在響，急忙關緊煤氣開關閥，同時打開屋內冷氣讓空氣流通。以為危機解除後，男子為了讓自己冷靜於是點燃香煙，豈料火花引燃了殘留在室內的爆氣，繼而引發爆炸。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上周四（2日）晚上11時許，平定縣公安局民警到場救援，消防大隊、安監局、住建局及煤氣公司等部門工作人員亦到場善後。初步調查指，住戶王男回到家中聽到煤氣報警器響，關閉煤氣閥後開冷氣，然後點燃香煙，在吸煙過程中引發燃爆。王男燒傷送院，無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n由於爆炸威力強勁，屋內損毀嚴重，所有窗戶都被震碎，附近的住戶也一度要疏散至安全地方。"},{"pid":"f3e17a38539195a07dbd2a94284d243e89c0dc4a","tid":772210,"uid":7940,"like":404,"dislike":4,"score":400,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏"},{"pid":"27733279a152702fc1afcc05e31b745bcd26d503","tid":772210,"uid":59832,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8237e3319017c416b8ec09a461cd8fdcde2d7d0","tid":772210,"uid":2223,"like":465,"dislike":3,"score":462,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"食支煙定定驚先！"},{"pid":"84e884c92de0f0497eb0d3078dddac523ad292c6","tid":772210,"uid":13308,"like":291,"dislike":3,"score":288,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<br />\n都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a130cd094102681466142042a1d70e2454b266","tid":772210,"uid":10845,"like":315,"dislike":5,"score":310,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T14:33:50.000Z","msg":"識得驚流煤氣。唔識得驚爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so